WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:00.633
Wow!

00:00:01.166 --> 00:00:01.600
You...

00:00:01.800 --> 00:00:02.366
Joseph!

00:00:02.366 --> 00:00:03.800
You two were...

00:00:04.266 --> 00:00:06.300
So when you said you were busy,

00:00:06.366 --> 00:00:07.566
you meant doing it

00:00:07.566 --> 00:00:08.800
with Charles in the...

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:09.800
restroom?

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:11.566
You got it wrong.

00:00:11.833 --> 00:00:13.033
He's straight.

00:00:13.766 --> 00:00:14.433
Hey.

00:00:14.633 --> 00:00:15.500
Just curious...

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.533
are you top or bottom?

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:20.133
Wait, can I put it that way?

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:20.600
Hey!

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:21.700
Are you the one inside

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:22.800
or outside?

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.200
Take one pill twice a day.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:26.500
Don't forget,

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:27.500
and don't take more.

00:00:31.366 --> 00:00:32.400
Vitamins?

00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:34.300
They're not meds.

00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:36.000
I changed the bottle.

00:00:36.366 --> 00:00:37.633
The club's packed.

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:42.800
You gotta be careful.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:44.966
Keep it low.

00:00:46.866 --> 00:00:47.700
Thanks, bro.

00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:50.966
Bro?

00:00:51.233 --> 00:00:52.633
To hell with that.

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:02.800
Is your sensitive spot...

00:01:03.533 --> 00:01:04.433
here?

00:01:06.733 --> 00:01:07.933
Or here?

00:01:12.133 --> 00:01:12.933
Or...

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:15.900
Watch your hand!

00:01:16.133 --> 00:01:17.633
I'll break your arms!

00:01:17.833 --> 00:01:19.200
When you have time,

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.066
stimulate these spots more.

00:01:21.100 --> 00:01:22.700
It helps with your condition.

00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:28.200
Add me on WeChat.

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:29.500
Let's keep in touch

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:31.500
and talk about your treatment.

00:01:35.966 --> 00:01:36.500
Gotta go.

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:40.033
Don't forget your 
follow-up!

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:41.500
Try to avoid

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:43.500
high-intensity training.

00:01:56.433 --> 00:01:56.800
Damn!

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.100
Are you freaking crazy?

